headline: Incyte Gets FDA Breakthrough Therapy Fast Track For Rare Blood Cancer Drug
summary: The FDA granted Breakthrough Therapy status to Incyte's experimental treatment for a rare blood cancer. Incyte stock is basing near five-year highs.
